Phase66Description:
Upon arriving at the statue of Tibault, I was set upon by distraught pilgrims. Apparently this one-eyed swordsman caused them great distress. 

Perhaps they know where Symon went next.
Name: To Walk a Dark Path
Toast: Zarbinzet's only priest is concerned for his missing curate.
Phase11Description:
Father Dymus, the priest of Zarbinzet has asked me to look for signs of his curate Symon who left on a journey with a stranger several weeks past. 

Symon's journal page says they were headed to a ruined farmstead to the east.
